{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/adsji5sn","slide":8,"name":"text","text":"- Pre-tokenizers are language-specific and brittle for scripts without spaces\n- The same pipeline can be used for Japanese, English, and multilingual corpora\n- Raw-text training helps make the tokenizer a reproducible model artifact","textPreview":"- Pre-tokenizers are language-specific and brittle for scripts without spaces | - The same pipeline can be used for Japanese, English, an...","textChars":232,"textLines":3,"bbox":[710,274,488,240]}
